BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260324T070600
DTEND:20260324T085400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.628ft at 07:06\n-0.008ft at 08:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 New round of fair size SW Southern Hemi slowly fills in\, along with some 
 secondary NW swell. By the afternoon good southerly exposures are running 
 waist to chest high\, while focal points hit head high\, largest late. Mid
  morning drained by a negative low tide\, then incoming tide push lends a 
 hand through the middle of the day.\n\nLight offshores early morning\, tur
 ning to light southerly onshores over the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260324T114800
DTEND:20260324T163000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.033ft at 11:48\n-2.983ft at 16:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 New round of fair size SW Southern Hemi slowly fills in\, along with some 
