BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260325T070600
DTEND:20260325T100000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.933ft at 07:06\n-0.054ft at 10:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Blend of long-period SW swell and steep-angled\, shorter-period NW swell e
 dges up through the day\, with waves getting into the waist-chest-shoulder
  high range at better breaks over the afternoon\, showing largest late. Mi
 d day negative low tide drains most spots\, then incoming tide push helps 
 during much of the afternoon. \n\nLight winds due through the day\, keepin
 g town at least semi-clean. 
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260325T131200
DTEND:20260325T172400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.01ft at 13:12\n-2.96ft at 17:24\n\nOBSERVATION:\nBl
 end of long-period SW swell and steep-angled\, shorter-period NW swell edg
 es up through the day\, with waves getting into the waist-chest-shoulder h
 igh range at better breaks over the afternoon\, showing largest late. Mid 
 day negative low tide drains most spots\, then incoming tide push helps du
 ring much of the afternoon. \n\nLight winds due through the day\, keeping 
